title: AdMuncher 4.71.28140
description:
One of the best popup / banner detector and remover

Ad Muncher is a program for Windows systems which removes adverts, popups and other annoying things from all popular browsers, as well as most banner displaying and popup generating programs like ICQ, Morpheus, Kazaa, Grokster, Opera, PalTalk, iMesh, Bearshare, LimeWire, etc. What can Ad Muncher do for you?
